description: When a rogue vampire kills his partner, an NSA special agent reluctantly teams with another officer who is a "good" vampire in an attempt to track down the evil vampire killer.
keywords: euro trash,trash movie,z movie,exploitation film,female rear nudity
name: The Breed

review.name: Cool Movie
review.reviewBody:
Despite what other people wrote, this is a pretty decent movie. It has some damn cool ideas and scenes. Even though i'd call it more of a Vampire Scifi, people who like and appreciate horror movies should definatly watch this. 6.5/10 Compared to the crap that's out there, this is one of the better ones.

About movies in general; There's no such thing as ripping off The Matrix ,Tarantino, or any other "ripped off" movies. Just because it's popular, doesn't mean its original. Every movie ripps off every movie.
